    "is_good_patch": true,
    "synth_pr": "\n## Title: Fix address sanitizer errors in LDPC encoder functions\n\n### Summary\nThe NR LDPC encoder functions for BG1 (ldpc176_byte through ldpc384_byte) were causing address sanitizer errors during execution. These functions use complex indexing patterns that appear to access memory beyond array bounds but are actually valid within their SIMD operations context.\n\nThis fix adds the missing `__attribute__ ((no_sanitize(\"address\", \"undefined\")))` to all BG1 LDPC encoder functions to prevent false positive sanitizer errors.\n\n### Reproduction\nWhen running OAI5G with address sanitization enabled and Zc=208 (or other BG1 configurations), the following error occurs:\n\n```\nERROR: AddressSanitizer: stack-buffer-overflow on address 0x7fff5fbff000 at pc 0x7ffff7b8c000\nREAD of size 16 at 0x7fff5fbff000 thread T0\n    #0 0x7ffff7b8c000 in ldpc208_byte /repo/openair1/PHY/CODING/nrLDPC_encoder/ldpc208_byte.c:14\n```\n\nThe issue manifests as unexpected behavior or crashes when encoding with BG1 configurations, particularly when Zc >= 176.\n\n### Changes\n- `openair1/PHY/CODING/nrLDPC_encoder/ldpc176_byte.c`: Added no_sanitize attribute\n- `openair1/PHY/CODING/nrLDPC_encoder/ldpc192_byte.c`: Added no_sanitize attribute  \n- `openair1/PHY/CODING/nrLDPC_encoder/ldpc208_byte.c`: Added no_sanitize attribute\n- `openair1/PHY/CODING/nrLDPC_encoder/ldpc224_byte.c`: Added no_sanitize attribute\n- `openair1/PHY/CODING/nrLDPC_encoder/ldpc240_byte.c`: Added no_sanitize attribute\n- `openair1/PHY/CODING/nrLDPC_encoder/ldpc256_byte.c`: Added no_sanitize attribute\n- `openair1/PHY/CODING/nrLDPC_encoder/ldpc288_byte.c`: Added no_sanitize attribute\n- `openair1/PHY/CODING/nrLDPC_encoder/ldpc320_byte.c`: Added no_sanitize attribute\n- `openair1/PHY/CODING/nrLDPC_encoder/ldpc352_byte.c`: Added no_sanitize attribute\n- `openair1/PHY/CODING/nrLDPC_encoder/ldpc384_byte.c`: Added no_sanitize attribute\n- `openair1/PHY/CODING/nrLDPC_encoder/ldpc192_byte_128.c`: Added no_sanitize attribute\n- `openair1/PHY/CODING/nrLDPC_encoder/ldpc224_byte_128.c`: Added no_sanitize attribute\n- `openair1/PHY/CODING/nrLDPC_encoder/ldpc240_byte_128.c`: Added no_sanitize attribute\n- `openair1/PHY/CODING/nrLDPC_encoder/ldpc256_byte_128.c`: Added no_sanitize attribute\n- `openair1/PHY/CODING/nrLDPC_encoder/ldpc288_byte_128.c`: Added no_sanitize attribute\n- `openair1/PHY/CODING/nrLDPC_encoder/ldpc320_byte_128.c`: Added no_sanitize attribute\n- `openair1/PHY/CODING/nrLDPC_encoder/ldpc352_byte_128.c`: Added no_sanitize attribute\n- `openair1/PHY/CODING/nrLDPC_encoder/ldpc384_byte_128.c`: Added no_sanitize attribute\n"
}